Two explosions occur in the southern Yemeni city of Aden, killing one person and injuring several others. The Al-Qaeda offshoot in the country also states its intention to establish a "new army" to overthrow the President. (BBC) (Al Jazeera) (Voice of Russia)Russian and American forces conduct their first joint anti-narcotics operation in Afghanistan. (RIA Novosti) (Reuters) (The Hindu)